original_title: AC/DC - Capital Center, Landover, MD, USA, December 1981
overview: AC/DC performing live at Capital Center, Landover, Maryland, USA and shot across December 20th and 21st of 1981 during the For Those About To Rock tour.  01) Put The Finger On You; 02) Back In Black; 03) Highway To Hell; 04) Let's Get It Up; 05) Let There Be Rock; 06) For Those About To Rock (We Salute You); 07) T.N.T.
title: AC/DC - Capital Center, Landover, MD, USA, December 1981
